These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: drama, superhero, mystery, scientific, family, western, adventure
 1. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
 2. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person watching family movies##7
 3. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person watching drama movies##7
 4. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
 5. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person watching western movies##8
 6. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 8. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person watching adventure movies##7
 9. the person watching mystery movies is not to the right of the person watching scientific movies##8
10. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | drama | superhero | mystery | scientific | western | adventure |

