.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, weightlifting, cricket, surfing, handball, rowing, ice-hockey
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
 4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 6. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
10. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| Sport   | surfing | weightlifting | rowing | ice-hockey | cricket | basketball | handball |

