.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: writing, baking, rock-climbing, skydiving, fishing, board-games, card-games
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##8
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is baking##7
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Hobby   | fishing | board-games | skydiving | card-games | writing | rock-climbing | baking |

