 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
 6. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
 9. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking cola##2
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2    |       3       |    4     |      5      |  6   |    7     |
| Beverage   | 7up | sprite | coffee | soy-milk | tea | cola | water |

