 2. the person driving the helicopter is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
 3. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 5. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the person driving the tram##8
 6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
 8. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the person driving the subway##8
10. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
11. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
12. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
13. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
14. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2      |     3      |  4  |    5    |   6   |    7    |
| Transport   | taxi | subway | helicopter | motorbike | bike | van | tram |

